      "raw_text": "Suit was commenced this afternoon\nin the superior court by the city\nagainst the Washington Water Power\ncompany to have the franchise given\nto the company on September 10,\n1890, to operate a street car line on\nThird avenue between Howard and\nNapa streets declared void The city\ncoqtends that the company has let the\nfranchise lapse as it did no work on\nthe proposed line."
